Product Description

Bumkins Grande Diaper Bag is the perfect tote for carrying all of mom and baby's needs! Functional and fashionable this eye-catching bag features generous sizing reinforced straps and waterproof lining . Reinforced straps ensure the bag can tote a substantial load to accommodate all of baby's needs. Rounded metal loops add additional storage possibilities and carrying versatility; it is easy to attach keys stroller straps and carabiners. Durable easy-wipe screenprinted exterior graphic makes a fashionable statement. Three exterior pockets including one large front pocket with velcro closure keep necessary items within easy reach. Five interior pockets allow mom and baby's items to stay organized and easily accessible. Includes matching waterproof change pad.
